marketing: PENNZOIL MARINE^® PREMIUM PLUS OUTBOARD TWO-CYCLE OIL contains only ashless components which helps prevent any lubricant related preignition and spark plug fouling. The ashless additives also help protect against piston and combustion chamber deposits, rust, and corrosion. It’s “anti-gel” properties help resist gel formation due to water or other contamination. The special base stocks used resist piston and cylinder wall scuffing.
